# #Misfits Change
# Radiation ambient warning messages — sent privately to the irradiated player only.
# Appear in the local chat box with no name attached (like a /do or subtle admin prayer).

# Tier 0 — mild exposure (faint unease, >0.05 rads/s)
rad-warning-tier0-a = Something about this place makes you deeply uneasy.
rad-warning-tier0-b = You feel a faint chill that has nothing to do with the temperature.
rad-warning-tier0-c = The air here feels... wrong. You can't quite explain it.

# Tier 1 — moderate exposure (nausea / headache, >0.40 rads/s)
rad-warning-tier1-a = A wave of nausea washes over you. You should not linger here.
rad-warning-tier1-b = Your head begins to pound. Something in this place is making you sick.
rad-warning-tier1-c = Your stomach turns. The air tastes metallic and stale.

# Tier 2 — significant exposure (skin burns / hair loss, >1.00 rads/s)
rad-warning-tier2-a = You notice loose strands of hair on your sleeve. Your skin feels raw.
rad-warning-tier2-b = Your gums are beginning to ache. Your body is warning you to move.
rad-warning-tier2-c = A deep, burning sensation crawls under your skin. This place will hurt you.

# Tier 3 — severe exposure (imminent death, >2.50 rads/s)
rad-warning-tier3-a = Every instinct tells you this place will kill you. Leave. Now.
rad-warning-tier3-b = You can feel your body deteriorating. Your vision blurs at the edges.
rad-warning-tier3-c = Your hair is coming out in clumps. Your organs feel like they are on fire.
